keyMappings:
map e scrollUp
map E previousTab

map n scrollDown
map N nextTab

map k performFind
map K performBackwardsFind

map h goBack
map i goForward

map o Vomnibar.activateBookmarksInNewTab
map t Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
map : Vomnibar.activateInNewTab

g: https://www.google.com/search?q=%s Google
y: https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=%s Youtube
